Box 289, 127 Highway 42 East, Bedford, KY 40006 Office Hours are 9:00 a.m. to 12:00 p.m. Monday and Friday, 19289=In a special meeting Monday, Trimble County Fiscal Court approved a $71,800 bid from Harp Enterprises to supply the county with 15 paper-ballot scanning machines and 13 compatible direct-reading electronic voting machines, which will be used by county voters in the May Primary. Harp was the sole bidder. The package also contains a desktop PC and a laptop PC and other peripherals, as well as maintenance and preparation for each election. No additional maintenance fees are involved., 32336=Copyright © 2015}
